title: The title of hyperlink builder should be 'Hyperlink Options', but it changes with settings.
OB: When setting a label hyperlink as 'www.actuate.com'
EB: The title of the hyperlink builder should be 'Hyperlink Options'.
SR:
To reproduce this issue, follow these steps:
1. Set a label hyperlink as 'www.actuate.com'.
2. Confirm that the title of the hyperlink builder is 'Hyperlink Options'.
